bdullah ibn Amr, and I said, \u201cNarrate to me what you have heard from the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d Abdullah set out a scroll, and he said, \u201cThis is what the Messenger of Allah has written for me.\u201d I\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18328,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/02\/supplication-dua-morning-evening\/","url_meta":{"origin":18465,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: All praise is due to Allah, morning and evening","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 2, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say during the evening, \u201cWe have entered the evening and so has the dominion of Allah. All praise is due to Allah, there is no God but Allah alone without any partners.\u201d I think the Prophet said\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26463,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/05\/28\/dua-abu-bakr-morning-evening\/","url_meta":{"origin":18465,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Abu Bakr\u2019s supplication for morning, evening, sleep","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 28, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: Abu Bakr, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, instruct me with something to say in the mornings and evenings.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cS